BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION [`V=kr^3\text{,}`] and solving for [`k`] we find that [`k=\dfrac{4}{3}\pi\text{,}`] so [`V=\dfrac{4}{3}\pi r^3`]
END_PGML_SOLUTION
